---
/**
 * EncryptionCompare.astro
 * At rest vs in transit comparison
 */
---

<div class="enc-wrap">
  <h3 class="enc-title">Encryption — At Rest vs In Transit</h3>
  <div class="enc-grid">
    <div class="enc-card" style="--i:0; --color:#818cf8;">
      <div class="enc-badge">At Rest</div>
      <div class="enc-desc">Protects stored data: databases, disks, backups, S3 buckets</div>
      <div class="enc-how">
        <div class="enc-step">Data → Encrypt with AES-256 → Store ciphertext</div>
        <div class="enc-step">Retrieve ciphertext → Decrypt with key → Data</div>
      </div>
      <div class="enc-tools">KMS, LUKS, BitLocker, dm-crypt, Transparent Data Encryption</div>
      <div class="enc-protects">Protects against: disk theft, unauthorized storage access, backup exposure</div>
    </div>
    <div class="enc-card" style="--i:1; --color:#4ade80;">
      <div class="enc-badge">In Transit</div>
      <div class="enc-desc">Protects moving data: API calls, browser traffic, service-to-service</div>
      <div class="enc-how">
        <div class="enc-step">Client → TLS handshake → Encrypted channel</div>
        <div class="enc-step">Data flows encrypted → Decrypted at destination</div>
      </div>
      <div class="enc-tools">TLS 1.3, mTLS, HTTPS, VPN, WireGuard, SSH tunnels</div>
      <div class="enc-protects">Protects against: eavesdropping, MITM attacks, packet sniffing</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="enc-both">
    <div class="enc-both-label">🔐 Both Required</div>
    <div class="enc-both-text">Encryption at rest without in transit = data encrypted on disk but sent in cleartext over the wire. In transit without at rest = data encrypted during transfer but readable by anyone with disk access.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .enc-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0}
  .enc-title{color:#f1f5f9;text-align:center;font-size:1.25rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .enc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
  @media(max-width:640px){.enc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .enc-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--color);border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;opacity:0;animation:encFade .5s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.2s)}
  @keyframes encFade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
  .enc-badge{background:var(--color);color:#0f172a;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;padding:.15rem .5rem;border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .enc-desc{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:.75rem}
  .enc-how{background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:.6rem .75rem;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .enc-step{color:#06b6d4;font-family:monospace;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6}
  .enc-tools{color:#f59e0b;font-size:.75rem;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .enc-protects{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.78rem}
  .enc-both{background:rgba(245,158,11,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);border-radius:10px;padding:1rem}
  .enc-both-label{color:#f59e0b;font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:.3rem}
  .enc-both-text{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.8rem;line-height:1.5}
</style>
